				<a href='/eq/view_profile?user.id=25491' class="auth_text" style="font-weight:bold;"><img src='/i/rank_icons/moderator.gif' border=0 alt=''> <span style='color:#FF0000;font-weight:bold; '>Ashlanne</span></a>
